<subSubSection id="D3C2089C6F76FFBC4DBAACA4FAE5FA1B" box="[199,1316,1410,1435]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="9B675B176F76FFBC4DBAACA4FAE5FA1B" blockId="6.[151,1437,1158,2011]" box="[199,1316,1410,1435]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181">
<emphasis id="A9AC87056F76FFBC4DBAACA4FE8FFA1B" bold="true" box="[199,334,1410,1435]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181">Etymology.</emphasis>
Soligena (Latin)—born by the sun—because of the pale (sunburn) wing ground colour.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D3C2089C6F76FFBC4DBAAC80FCE3F917" pageId="6" pageNumber="181" type="description">
<paragraph id="9B675B176F76FFBC4DBAAC80FCE3F917" blockId="6.[151,1437,1158,2011]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181">
<emphasis id="A9AC87056F76FFBC4DBAAC80FE98FA3F" bold="true" box="[199,345,1446,1471]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181">Description.</emphasis>
<collectingCountry id="E3CF1B876F76FFBC4C1DAC80FE5FFA3F" box="[352,414,1446,1471]" name="Malta" pageId="6" pageNumber="181">Male</collectingCountry>
. Forewing length 
<quantity id="5C20F6F26F76FFBC4F17AC81FD26FA3E" box="[618,743,1447,1471]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.8" pageId="6" pageNumber="181" unit="mm" value="19.0" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="18.0">18–20 mm</quantity>
. Forewing ground colour brownish-grey, orange at basal 
<number id="2D1049306F76FFBC480DAC80FABAFA3F" box="[1392,1403,1446,1471]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number id="2D1049306F76FFBC48FAAC80FA56FA3F" box="[1415,1431,1446,1471]" pageId="6" pageNumber="181" value="5.0">5</number>
; basal part of costal margin black. Outer part of the forewing yellow with variable saturations, from pale yellow to orange; in any case reduction of dark grey suffusion is typical for this subspecies. Hindwings light yellow, with greyish costal area. Fore wing cilia grey, hind wing cilia yellow. 
<collectingCountry id="E3CF1B876F76FFBC4EE8AF34FC0EF9AB" box="[917,975,1554,1579]" name="Malta" pageId="6" pageNumber="181">Male</collectingCountry>
genitalia (
